This program's depends on the POSIX specification and, optionally, OpenCL. 

To compile with OpenCL support, type: 

make opencl

To compile without OpenCL support, type:

make nocl

To compile both (with test cases) type:

make

To invoke the program, execute either

./des 

or 

./des_cl

Arguments are optional, first argument is the number of keys and the second (nocl only) is for the number of threads to instantiate.

